    public class TeleportCell
extends AbstractCell
    TeleportCell represents a cell where the Player is teleported to another cell upon arrival.

      • handleMove

        public int handleMove(int diceThrow)
        Description copied from interface: ICell
        Returns the index of the cell actually reached by a Player when he reaches this cell. For normal cells, the returned value equals ICell.getIndex() and is thus independent from diceThrow.
        Parameters:
        diceThrow - The result of the dice when the player reaches this cell.
        Returns:
        The index of the cell effectively reached when a player reaches this cell after the given throw of dice.
